==  Lajiide (Somali: Lajiide, [[File:Lajiide carabi.png|thumb]]
 waa dagmo ku taalo gobolka Galgaduud ee bartamaha Somalia . Dadka deggan degmada Lajiide, waxay u badan yihin xoolo dhaqato. Lajiide waxaa si Gaar ah u daga beesha reer Guuled Agoon.  ==
Lajiide  is a town located in the central Galgaduud area of Somalia. the town primarily inhabited by Dir specially sub-clan of Rar Agoon  Surre (clan). The city is located near the border of Ethiopia about 20 km South and 30km West of Abudwaq.
